:13:10.000Z","msg":"殖民9劃國界"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"其實我一路都好奇依樣野<br />\n非洲D國家都唔係跟民族而劃既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b37282557ffab29cf29ab24344398ee87c63a7","tid":2460702,"uid":241399,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:16:48.000Z","msg":"其實非洲好多地方同支那二三線城市差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVKxJu7YSp6syT54qr21KSvvZVrMkK9GvFKedDTpGXtFr?filename=RcYPhVa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcYPhVa.png&h=5b2a6482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6865c0710623d62a4d4cb42e43e701f0d21aaa98","tid":2460702,"uid":61882,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"f563849158a50cfbaa64889349f45f67f3f60d24","tid":2460702,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba1016d33b13f8db52820abeb6dbbe6e949d3482","tid":2460702,"uid":195338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"殖民9劃國界"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"其實我一路都好奇依樣野<br />\n非洲D國家都唔係跟民族而劃既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/72e6a31990164e859a3db51b7658b83f_18.jpeg?resize=770%2C513\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F72e6a31990164e859a3db51b7658b83f_18.jpeg%3Fresize%3D770%252C513&h=1b4cb1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1884年柏林剛果會議<br />\n俾斯麥主持嘅切餅大會<br />\n成個會唯一一個去過非洲嘅人叫亨利&middot;莫頓&middot;史坦利<br />\n一個幫比利時國王做嘢嘅美國探險家<br />\n喺冇代表非洲人利益嘅人參與下<br />\n非洲入面唔同種族經過幾千年自然演化出嚟嘅勢力範圍自然就會被忽略啦<br />\n切餅前各部族嘅勢力範圍<br />\n<img src=\"http://voxeu.org/sites/default/files/image/FromAug2010/PapaFig1a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvoxeu.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimage%2FFromAug2010%2FPapaFig1a.gif&h=830dfc9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係切餅嘅結果喇<br />\n<img src=\"http://solarey.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/africa-seperations.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsolarey.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F10%2Fafrica-seperations.jpg&h=608e86e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話明係切餅當然就有好多直線啦<br />\n呢啲直線往往會將敵對嘅種族劃埋一齊<br />\n又或者將同一個種族分開喺唔同嘅國家<br />\n咁好自然敵對嘅勢力會互相鬥爭<br />\n相同嘅種族又會試圖合併<br />\n自此以後成個非洲大陸就成為咗一部特大號嘅攪肉機<br />\n當歐洲殖民者夠實力時都仲壓得住佢地嘅<br />\n但兩次大戰後佢地再冇餘力睇住個場喇<br />\n民族主義抬頭再加上共產國際喺後面推波助瀾<br />\n非洲人慢慢就成為咗人類嘅毒瘤喇(好似係)"},{"pid":"718b7fd8bfa2f0fa30595b4e53fec910a435e91a","tid":2460702,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"其實點解要解決非洲問題<br />\n非洲有好吸引嘅資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff03edeb017ad4d7b3a9036f211d8ee0b409553d","tid":2460702,"uid":218158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"718b7fd8bfa2f0fa30595b4e53fec910a435e91a","tid":2460702,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"其實點解要解決非洲問題<br />\n非洲有好吸引嘅資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"係，佢有大量人口，大量自然資源，而且佢上面接地中海，左面接大西洋，右面係印度洋，個地緣位置好多國家都想攞着數，發展到嘅話個潛力絕對勁過支那<br />\n<br />\n詳細可以睇下依兩條片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dqRVlGFNn60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdqRVlGFNn60&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=3a6193e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dqRVlGFNn60</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NbKoXlYUNY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNbKoXlYUNY0&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=f213e16c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NbKoXlYUNY0</a>"},{"pid":"37431477e9ab64008791376df08c825b3cd0061e"